Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: "Let me also deliver a message straight to Kamala Harris, the radical left Democrats politicians, and Fake News media -- It's time to stop the lies, stop the hoaxes, stop the smears, stop the lawfare and stop claiming your opponents will turn America into a dictatorship. Because the fact is I'm not threat to democracy. They are."
